            <!-- Section 3: Wallet Compatibility -->
            <section class="content-section" id="compatibility">
                <h2 class="section-heading">Seamless Ecosystem Integration</h2>
                <p>
                    <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong> acts as a secure shield for the wallet software you already use. While your regular wallet tracks your balances, <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong> keeps your private keys completely offline and out of reach.
                </p>
                <p>
                    To use it, just move a transaction file over using a QR code or USB, sign it while you&rsquo;re offline, and send it back to your regular wallet to finish. Your keys stay totally disconnected from the internet, exactly where they belong.
                </p>
                <h3 class="subsection-heading">Advanced Multisig Coordination</h3>
                <p>
                    <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong> makes multi-signature setups easy without forcing you to buy multiple hardware devices. You can sign with your main key, then temporarily load extra keys to finish the transaction. These extra keys only stay in the system's short-term memory; the moment you finish or turn off the power, they are wiped completely and forever.
                </p>
                <h3 class="subsection-heading">Native Compatibility</h3>
                <ul class="spec-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="spec-label">Sparrow Wallet</span>
                        <span class="spec-desc">Use Sparrow on your desktop to track your balances and organize transactions. When it’s time to sign, Sparrow hands the job off to <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong>—keeping your keys offline while you move data back and forth using simple files or QR codes.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="spec-label">Electrum</span>
                        <span class="spec-desc">Easily connect your cold storage to Electrum. <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong> creates wallet files that Electrum recognizes instantly. It also uses Electrum’s QR standards, so you can scan and go without needing to convert any files yourself.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="spec-label">Nunchuk</span>
                        <span class="spec-desc">The perfect setup for your phone. <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong> works seamlessly with Nunchuk’s QR-based system. It’s a fast "scan-and-send" experience that keeps your mobile signing simple and secure.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="spec-label">Blue Wallet</span>
                        <span class="spec-desc">Keep an eye on your money from anywhere. You can import your public info into Blue Wallet to check your balance on the go, while the actual power to spend stays safely locked inside</strong>.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="spec-label">Specter Desktop</span>
                        <span class="spec-desc">A natural fit for multisig-first setups. <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong> exports descriptors and PSBTs in the formats Specter expects, making it straightforward to coordinate complex signing arrangements without ever exposing a key to an online machine.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
